(42, 445, 'XRF is safe po ba? Do we have an assurance if the user will use it? May chance po ba na ito ay makapahamak?\n', 'Nuclear Analytical Techniques Applications Section', 'Yes, XRF is safe to use. The instrument itself is designed with safety in mind. Additionally, users of XRF are required to undergo training before they are given authorization to use the machine.', '2021-12-09 12:42:53'),
(43, 445, 'None\n', 'Philippine Research Reactor - 1', 'Thank you for your comment! We hope you enjoyed the virtual tour! To know more about our upcoming events, like us on Facebook (https://fb.me/PNRIDOST). You may also visit us at our website: www.pnri.dost.gov.ph Keep exploring!', '2021-12-09 12:43:38'),
