(52, 526, 'How to be sure that the products are fully sterilized? are there instances where there are radiation-resistant microbes found on the products?', 'Cobalt-60 Multipurpose Irradiation Facility', 'Hi! Thank you for your question. products after irradiation are sent to a microbiological lab to check if products are already sterile.  Regarding radiation-resistant microbes. It\'s a case-to-case basis, and usually, products are studied first before it is subjected to irradiation. ', '2021-12-09 18:21:27'),
