(55, 537, 'Do you accept visit tours for group of students who are interested in the field of research in the near future? If yes, what are the things we need to bring and steps to do before admission?', 'Nuclear Administration, Regulatory and Training Building', 'Thank you for your interest in visiting PNRI. Unfortunately, the institution is closed for visitors at the moment due to the pandemic. We look forward to see you face to face someday. In the meantime, you may learn more about us through our website www.pnri.dost.gov.ph or explore more videos of our events and activities through our YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChW6K3k2iSAc1Om_ivERaeQ.', '2021-12-09 18:51:57'),
(56, 538, 'Is the monument real? If so, where?', 'General Medina Monument', 'The General Medina Monument is real, and it is located inside the PNRI compound in Quezon City. :)', '2021-12-09 18:58:16'),
(57, 538, 'Can I join here?\n', 'Nuclear Administration, Regulatory and Training Building', 'There are many ways to get involved with PNRI. You may - (a) apply for intership/OJT, if you are a student; (b) participate in any of our training courses; (c) collaborate with PNRI on research, education or outreach activities; (d) find thesis/research adviser among the roster of PNRI researchers and scientists; or (e) apply in one of the vacant positions in the institution. Visit www.pnri.dost.gov.ph to learn more.', '2021-12-09 18:59:51'),
(58, 537, 'Ayon sa video na pinakita nyo ay binanggit na maraming ospital ang gumagamit ng Tc99m sa pagtukoy ng mga karamdaman. Nais ko pong malaman kung may access ba ang mga ospital sa probinsya ng Tc99m?', 'Technetium-99M Generator Facility', 'Yes, hospitals outside of Metro Manila may also avail of this service.', '2021-12-09 19:02:25'),
(59, 537, 'How frequent do you check the SOMER to gather data?', 'System for Online Monitoring of Environmental Radiation (SOMER)', NULL, '2021-12-09 19:11:18'),
(60, 537, 'Are all products available in the supermarket undergo to PNRI laboratory test?', 'Nuclear Analytical Techniques Applications Section', 'No, not all products available in the supermarket goes to PNRI for testing. This is due to factors such the type of test needed by the manufacturer and the regulations involved in the process.', '2021-12-09 19:23:46'),
(61, 537, 'Maari na po ba agad iconsume ang foods after irradiation or it takes time before po puwedeng iconsume dahil naexpose ito sa radiation.', 'Cobalt-60 Multipurpose Irradiation Facility', 'Magandang araw!  Maraming salamat sa iyong katanungan. Maari na po gamitin ang mga pagkain matapos itong ma-irradiate. Higit pa duon mas safe na ito kainin o gamitin dahil na sterilize na ang mga ito.  ', '2021-12-09 19:30:35'),
