(65, 537, 'Do you accept visit tours for group of students who are interested in the field of research in the near future? If yes, what are the things we need to bring and steps to do before admission?', 'Nuclear Administration, Regulatory and Training Building', 'Thank you for your interest in visiting PNRI. Unfortunately, the institution is closed for visitors at the moment due to the pandemic. We look forward to see you face to face someday. In the meantime, you may learn more about us through our website www.pnri.dost.gov.ph or explore more videos of our events and activities through our YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UChW6K3k2iSAc1Om_ivERaeQ.', '2021-12-09 20:38:45'),
